<h1 id="toc0"><span>MALICEAFORETHOUGHT'S ARTWORK PAGE!</span></h1>
</div>
<p>Wow, look at this, a bunch of pieces of 'art' that past versions of myself thought were worthy of being uploaded to the internet. Thanks, previous me! <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I'm not yet settled on a style, so join me on this journey through the wonderful world of medium-quality fanart&#8230;</span> Style's an odd thing, eh? I'm certainly more consistent than I used to be, but I still vary in terms of perspective, medium, and&#8230; pretty much everything else. Medium-quality is still right, but hopefully I've settled on the right side of mediocre.</p>
<p>Suggestions are always welcome!</p>
